net.floodlightcontroller.staticentry

类 StaticEntryPusher

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.staticentry.StaticEntryPusher
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IListener<org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.OFType>, IOFMessageListener, IOFSwitchListener, IFloodlightModule, IFloodlightService, IStaticEntryPusherService, IStorageSourceListener

    public class StaticEntryPusher
extends java.lang.Object
implements IOFSwitchListener, IFloodlightModule, IStaticEntryPusherService, IStorageSourceListener, IOFMessageListener
    This module is responsible for maintaining a set of static flows on switches. This is just a big 'ol dumb list of flows and groups and something external is responsible for ensuring they make sense for the network.

      • sendEntriesToSwitch

        protected void sendEntriesToSwitch(org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.DatapathId switchId)
        Reads from our entriesFromStorage for the specified switch and sends the FlowMods down to the controller in sorted order. Sorted is important to maintain correctness of the switch: if a packet would match both a lower and a higher priority rule, then we want it to match the higher priority or nothing, but never just the lower priority one. Inserting from high to low priority fixes this. TODO consider adding a "block all" flow mod and then removing it while starting up.
        参数:
        sw - The switch to send entries to

      • switchPortChanged

        public void switchPortChanged(org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.DatapathId switchId,
                              org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.OFPortDesc port,
                              PortChangeType type)
        从接口复制的说明: IOFSwitchListener
        Fired when a port on a known switch changes. A user of this notification needs to take care if the port and type information is used directly and if the collection of ports has been queried as well. This notification will only be dispatched after the the port changes have been committed to the IOFSwitch instance. However, if a user has previously called IOFSwitch.getPorts() or related method a subsequent update might already be present in the information returned by getPorts.
        指定者:
        switchPortChanged 在接口中 IOFSwitchListener
